<H4>    Update on Chinapac </H4>

<F P=102> 40100070A Beijing CHINA DAILY (SCIENCE AND TECHNOLOGY 
SUPPLEMENT) in English 3 Jun 94 p 1 </F>

<F P=103> 40100070A </F>
