<H3> <TI>   Anhui: Building an East China Energy Base </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Anhui: Building an East China Energy Base </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94FE0608C Beijing RENMIN RIBAO OVERSEAS EDITION in Chinese 
