<H3> <TI>   `Electric Power Corridor' for the Southwest </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Electric Power Corridor' for the Southwest </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   946B0072A Beijing RENMIN RIBAO OVERSEAS EDITION in Chinese 
26 Mar 94 p 2 </F>

<F P=103> 946B0072A </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing RENMIN RIBAO OVERSEAS EDITION </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


