<H3> <TI>   Shanghai Becomes Nuclear Power Equipment Manufacturing Base </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shanghai Becomes Nuclear Power Equipment Manufacturing Base </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94FE0603B Shanghai WENHUI BAO in Chinese 9 Apr 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94FE0603B </F>
<F P=104>  Shanghai WENHUI BAO </F>
