<H3> <TI>   980-nm LD-Pumped EDFA with Bandwidth Exceeding 40 nm </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    980-nm LD-Pumped EDFA with Bandwidth Exceeding 40 nm </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94P60282B Beijing GAO JISHU TONGXUN [HIGH TECHNOLOGY 
LETTERS] in Chinese Vol 4 No 2, Feb 94 pp 5-7 </F>

<F P=103> 94P60282B </F>
