<F P=106> [Article by Peng Jiangde, Jiang Xin [1203 2450] et al. of </F>
the Dept. of Electronic Engineering, Qinghua Univ., Beijing 
100084: ``Utilitarian 1.47-gmm LD-Pumped Er[.sup]3+[/]-Doped 
Fiber Optical Amplifier Module,'' supported by grant from 863 
Program; MS received 18 Nov 93. Cf. early brief report in 
