  [Abstract] The first domestic development of a utilitarian 
EDFA module prototype using two domestically made 25-mW, 
1480-nm-wavelength LDs as pump sources and 
Er[.sup]3+[/]/Al[.sup]3+[/] co-doped optical fiber is 
