  2. J. Nees, S. Williamson, and G. Mourou, APPL. PHYS. LETT., 
Vol 54, No 20, 1989, p 1962. 
  3. P. Uchmann, H. Kaufann, H. Melchior, and G. Guekos, APPL. 
PHYS. LETT., Vol 46, No 5, 1985, p 462. 
