<H3> <TI>   Italy: Infrared Sensor Developed for Environmental Monitoring </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italy: Infrared Sensor Developed for Environmental Monitoring </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MI2202104594 Milan CORRIERE DELLA SERA in Italian 23 Jan 94 
p 31--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> MI2202104594 </F>
<F P=104>  Milan CORRIERE DELLA SERA </F>
