<H3> <TI>   Italy: Government Establishes Environmental Agency </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Italy: Government Establishes Environmental Agency </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MI2202105194 Milan Il SOLE-24 ORE in Italian 13 Jan 94 p 
